 velocity of\n~238 km/s were identified in the jets. We carried out the DEM inversions to\ninvestigate the temperatures of the blobs, finding that the blobs were\nmultithermal with average temperature of 1.8$-$3.1 MK.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2016 03:19:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-13"}
