sible scenario for the system is that both\nof the planets have nearly circular orbits, namely the eccentricity of the\nouter planet is less than ~0.15, which is just within 1.4sigma of the best-fit\nvalue, or the planets are in a mutually retrograde configuration with a mutual\norbital inclination larger than 160 degree.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2016 07:27:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-16"}
