ght to the laboratory: tailored pump pulses can excite systems into\nlight-absorbing states. However, we also highlight the severe numerical and\ntheoretical difficulties posed by the problem: large-scale non-equilibrium\nquantum dynamics are cumbersome, even with TDDFT, and the shortcomings of\nstate-of-the-art TDDFT functionals may still be serious for these\nout-of-equilibrium situations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2016 14:48:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-22"}
